<a href="javascript:void(0);" onclick="AddFavorite('我是阴阳人  第665章 懂','http://www.wutuxs.com/html/1/1628/3308125.html')">收藏本文</a> | <a rel="nofollow" href="/modules/article/addbookcase.php?id=1628&amp;cid=3308125&amp;ajax_request=1" target="_blank">加入书签</a> | <a rel="nofollow" href="/modules/article/addbookcase.php?bid=1628&amp;cid=3308125" target="_blank">加入书架</a> | <a rel="nofollow" href="/modules/article/uservote.php?id=1628" target="_blank">推荐本书</a> | <a rel="nofollow" href="/newmessage.php?tosys=1&amp;title=我是阴阳人+ 第665章 懂+%D5%C2%BD%DA%B4%ED%CE%F3&amp;content=%B6%D4%B1%C8%CD%F8%D6%B7%CA%C7%A3%BA" target="_blank">错误举报</a> | <a href="http://m.wutuxs.com/html/1/1628/3308125.html" target="_blank" style="color:red">手机阅读</a></p><a href="http://www.wutuxs.com/">无图小说网</a> -&gt; <a href="/list/7_1.html">恐怖灵异</a> -&gt; <a href="/html/1/1628/">我是阴阳人</a> 小叙</dt><dd><h1> 第665章 懂</h1></dd>
